### Get lightbulb state
GET http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb

### Toggle lightbulb on/off
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/toggle

### Set color to red
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/color
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "red"
}

### Set color to green
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/color
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "green"
}

### Set color to blue
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/color
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "blue"
}

### Set color to yellow
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/color
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "yellow"
}

### Set color to white
POST http://localhost:8000/api/lightbulb/color
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "color": "white"
}
